{{Quote|Receiving data. Artoo said to tell you that he's doing it for Threepio, not for you.''"<br />"''I don't care if he does it for the Blood Prince of Thassalia, as long as it gets done.|[[Lobot/Legends|Lobot]] and [[Lando Calrissian/Legends|Lando Calrissian]]|<ref name="SoL">''[[Shield of Lies]]''</ref>}}
The '''Blood Prince of Thassalia''' was a [[Monarchy/Legends|monarchical]] title<ref name="SoL" /> that shared its name with the [[Thassalia system/Legends|Thassalia system]] of the [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|Outer Rim Territories']] [[Albanin sector/Legends|Albanin sector]].<ref name="EAOC">{{SW|url=news/star-wars-the-essential-atlas-online-companion|text=''Star Wars: The Essential Atlas'' Online Companion|int=Star Wars: The Essential Atlas Online Companion}}</ref>

{{Stub}}

==Behind the scenes==
The title of the Blood Prince of Thassalia was mentioned in ''[[Shield of Lies]]'', [[Michael P. Kube-McDowell]]'s [[1996]] first entry in ''[[The Black Fleet Crisis]]'' trilogy of novels.<ref name="SoL" />

